{"id":37825,"date":"2022-06-10T00:26:53","date_gmt":"2022-06-09T20:26:53","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=37825"},"modified":"2025-01-23T12:45:47","modified_gmt":"2025-01-23T08:45:47","slug":"sahaba-pledge-loyalty","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/06\/10\/sahaba-pledge-loyalty\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Bay\u2019ah: Companions pledge their loyalty to Islam"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: I pledged allegiance to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, along with a group of people. The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>I take your pledge that you will not associate partners with Allah, you will not steal, you will not commit adultery, you will not kill your children, you will not bring forth slander that you have fabricated, and you will not disobey me in good conduct. Whoever among you fulfills his pledge, his reward is with Allah. Whoever commits any of these sins, it will be taken from him in the world as his expiation and purification. Whoever has his crime concealed by Allah, then the matter belongs to Allah. If He wills, He will punish him, or if He wills, He will forgive him.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7468<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0639\u064f\u0628\u064e\u0627\u062f\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0645\u0650\u062a\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0627\u064a\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062a\u064f \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0641\u0650\u064a \u063